{
  "text": "Additionally, the survival outcomes in breast cancer survivors are likely to have some correlation with exercise intervention. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] However, the studies included in our current meta-analysis failed to examine this association. Therefore, it is recommended that future studies examine the effects of exercise intervention on survival outcomes and determine whether exercise will provide benefit to the survival outcomes.",
  "correct_citation": {
